## Limitations

The analysis is limited by the availability of recent data and the subjective nature of opinion pieces. Some sources may present biased views, and the lack of empirical data in certain articles could affect the comprehensiveness of the findings. Additionally, the rapidly changing landscape of digital advertising means that conclusions drawn from older sources may not fully reflect current trends and impacts.